{"id":232770319,"title":"體重機上的數字真的那麼重要嗎？","content":"很多人好像都很在意體重機上面的數字，我以我舉例\n⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️\nhttps://i.imgur.com/vSUEHbD.jpg\n左邊體重為80kg 右邊體重為78kg\n-\n因為肌肉量與體脂率不同而產生很大的視覺效果。\n體重會因為很多因素改變！好的減肥應該是去在意鏡子裡的體態而不是體重機上面的數字。\n剛開始減肥前我也是用了一堆莫名其妙的方法，得到只有一個不健康的身體🤷‍♂️，最後也是上了健身房請了教練。有了專業的指導才找到適合自己的方式。執行減重計劃前也要了解自身身體狀況，而不是用一些奇怪的方法（只吃一餐，代餐，減肥藥，水果減重，等等等等）把自己的身體搞的一團糟👌","excerpt":"很多人好像都很在意體重機上面的數字，我以我舉例，⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️，左邊體重為80kg 右邊體重為78kg，-，因為肌肉量與體脂率不同而產生很大的視覺效果。體重會因為很多因素改變","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"8a2a0b9a-7664-49b0-bff7-58389ef73a0d","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-27T07:14:02.305Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-27T07:16:58.844Z","commentCount":31,"likeCount":180,"tags":[],"topics":["數字","體重","減肥","減重","減脂"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"減肥","forumAlias":"weight_loss","school":"正修科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":178},{"id":"4b018f48-e184-445f-adf1-fc8e04ba09b9","count":1},{"id":"e8e6bc5d-41b0-4129-b134-97507523d7ff","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/vSUEHbD.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"59184683-973e-4171-a75d-71b39ba1ec53","url":"https://i.imgur.com/vSUEHbDl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/vSUEHbDl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/vSUEHbDl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED","GOOGLE_VISION_ADULT_LIKELY","SAFE"],"createdAt":"2019-12-27T07:14:02.305Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-27T07:16:58.844Z"},{"id":"59184683-973e-4171-a75d-71b39ba1ec53","url":"https://i.imgur.com/vSUEHbD.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/vSUEHbD","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/vSUEHbDl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED","GOOGLE_VISION_ADULT_LIKELY","SAFE"],"createdAt":"20